To quote [http://xfce.org/ xfce.org], Xfce is a lightweight desktop environment for Unix-like operating systems. It aims to be fast and low on system resources, while still being visually appealing and user friendly.

== Installation ==

=== Avoiding unnecessary dependencies ===

Avoiding optional GNOME support and packages will keep the system more lean and congruous.

Ensure that the system is using the basic "desktop" [[profile]]:

